10:07.740 --> 10:12.144
Now, class, I'd like to show you
what you can ultimately achieve.

10:12.245 --> 10:13.735
But I need somebody very strong

10:13.847 --> 10:15.644
and agile to help me
demonstrate.

10:15.748 --> 10:17.649
Don't look at me.
I can't even move.

10:17.750 --> 10:19.776
I'm too tired to even watch.

10:19.886 --> 10:22.787
Hey, Cunningham, I think
she's calling your number.

10:22.889 --> 10:24.914
Oh, no, no, Fonz, I think
she's talking about you.

10:25.024 --> 10:26.219
I don't think so.

10:26.326 --> 10:27.793
No, please, aren't you talking
about Fonzie?

10:27.894 --> 10:32.525
Yes. Come on, Mr. Fonzarelli,
you can be my partner.

10:32.632 --> 10:33.622
(all agreeing)

10:33.733 --> 10:35.292
I don't dance.

10:35.401 --> 10:37.893
- Come on.
- Yeah, come on, Fonz.

10:38.004 --> 10:39.369
Hey, hey! Whoa! No!

10:39.472 --> 10:40.940
POTSIE: Come on.
You can do anything.

10:41.040 --> 10:42.599
RICHIE:
Give it a shot.

10:42.709 --> 10:43.767
All right, I need room.

10:43.877 --> 10:46.675
- Yeah.
- All right!

10:46.779 --> 10:48.270
Now remember what I said.

10:48.381 --> 10:50.679
Are you kidding?
I'm gonna try.

10:50.783 --> 10:52.012
Chachi, music.

10:52.118 --> 10:53.984
All right.

10:54.087 --> 10:55.748
(orchestral music plays)

11:25.318 --> 11:27.218
