<i>II</i>

13:29.409 --> 13:31.400
<i>II</i>

14:07.113 --> 14:08.171
(all talking excitedly)

14:08.281 --> 14:09.840
All right,
that's enough for one day.

14:09.949 --> 14:11.815
- Yeah. -All right.
- Thanks for all coming.

14:11.918 --> 14:12.976
See you next week.

14:13.086 --> 14:14.212
- Okay. -Okay.
- Any homework?

14:14.320 --> 14:15.344
Oh, come on, Pots, please.

14:15.455 --> 14:16.718
Don't worry, Teach, I'll have

14:16.823 --> 14:19.292
the tutu cleaned and starched.

14:19.392 --> 14:20.985
I'm gonna grab a few
of those applications,

14:21.094 --> 14:22.891
and get me some partners.

14:22.995 --> 14:24.554
Wah, wah, wah.

14:24.664 --> 14:25.961
It must be the Fonzarelli blood.

14:26.065 --> 14:27.328
Hey, listen, you guys, uh,

14:27.433 --> 14:29.367
the dance stays in this room.

14:29.469 --> 14:31.460
- Yeah, all right.
- All right, Fonz, yeah.

14:32.672 --> 14:35.038
Thanks for the students, Fonz.

14:35.141 --> 14:36.074
Hey, wait a minute.

14:36.175 --> 14:37.074
You wanted a class,

14:37.176 --> 14:38.507
that was your first class.

14:38.611 --> 14:41.308
Hold on.

14:41.414 --> 14:43.348
All right, second class,
let's go.

14:43.449 --> 14:44.678
Come on, get in here.

14:44.784 --> 14:45.944
Hurry up, scoot it up!

14:49.288 --> 14:50.278
What are you gonna do?

14:50.389 --> 14:51.413
You gonna
wait there all day?

14:51.524 --> 14:53.788
Get in here.

14:53.893 --> 14:55.884
NQW!

14:59.632 --> 15:01.623
Hey, did you guys ever do this?

15:07.740 --> 15:09.333
Al, this has been
a pretty big week for you.

15:09.442 --> 15:11.410
I mean, first you're reffing
basketball games,

15:11.511 --> 15:13.035
then you're taking
a... a ballet class.

15:13.146 --> 15:15.512
I guess you must be
a little stiff, huh?

15:15.615 --> 15:16.673
Nah.

15:16.783 --> 15:17.841
Oh, that's terrific.

15:17.950 --> 15:19.748
Would you pass me
the salt, please?

15:25.391 --> 15:27.587
Al, get the salt, please?

15:27.693 --> 15:29.491
I'm passing it, Rich.

15:29.595 --> 15:32.463
Oh, well... here.

15:32.565 --> 15:34.590
- I guess I'm a little stiff.
- Yeah.

15:34.700 --> 15:36.794
(crashing in distance)

15:36.903 --> 15:39.235
Oh, no, trouble in the kitchen.

15:39.338 --> 15:41.330
I got to hurry up and get there.

15:46.412 --> 15:47.607
How you doing, Al?

15:47.713 --> 15:49.705
Not now, Fonz, I'm in a hurry.

15:52.185 --> 15:53.413
Yeah, it looks it, Al.

15:53.519 --> 15:54.611
It really looks it.

15:54.720 --> 15:55.881
- Hi, Fonz.
- Hey, listen.

15:55.988 --> 15:57.615
I got to ask you a favor,
Cunningham, all right?

15:57.723 --> 15:58.816
- Sure. -It's a little
chilly out and I want

15:58.925 --> 16:00.222
to take Colleen for a ride.

16:00.326 --> 16:01.452
Can I borrow your car?

16:01.561 --> 16:03.188
Oh sure.
Well, I-l have to drop off

16:03.296 --> 16:04.490
some homework at Lori Beth's.

16:04.597 --> 16:05.826
But I'll be right back.

16:05.932 --> 16:07.126
Well, unless, of course, uh,

16:07.233 --> 16:09.565
Lori Beth attacks me.
(laughs)

16:09.669 --> 16:11.330
Yeah, well, look, uh,
if she does,

16:11.437 --> 16:12.768
don't surrender this time,
all right?

16:12.872 --> 16:14.806
I want to make
my little butterfly happy.

16:14.907 --> 16:15.806
Yeah, okay, Fonz.

16:15.908 --> 16:17.035
All right, thanks.

16:17.143 --> 16:18.303
Oh, Fonz, uh, wait a minute.

16:18.411 --> 16:19.605
- There's...
- Yeah, what do you want?

16:19.712 --> 16:21.146
