to teach it.

17:16.535 --> 17:18.595
You practice it to do it, bucko!

17:18.704 --> 17:20.400
Bucko?

17:20.506 --> 17:21.701
Hey, let me tell you something.

17:21.807 --> 17:23.069
When it comes to knowing chicks,

17:23.175 --> 17:24.837
one of us has got
a slight edge, huh?

17:24.944 --> 17:26.502
Okay, Mr. Slight Edge,
how come you don't know

17:26.612 --> 17:28.012
that she wants to perform?

17:28.114 --> 17:29.809
There's a lot I know,
and the first thing I know

17:29.916 --> 17:31.907
is not to take advice from you.

17:34.654 --> 17:37.123
A lot of people
take advice from me!

17:37.223 --> 17:40.352
You don't see Joanie
wearing pigtails, do you?

17:43.996 --> 17:45.987
Why did I say that?

