I'm sorry I'm not ready yet.

20:33.332 --> 20:34.493
Believe me...

20:34.600 --> 20:36.227
you're ready.

20:36.335 --> 20:37.427
Okay?

20:37.536 --> 20:41.063
Dancing looks
so beautiful on you.

20:41.173 --> 20:43.699
Why don't you go
to New York and perform?

20:43.809 --> 20:45.937
New York?!

20:46.045 --> 20:48.104
You love to dance, don't you?

20:48.214 --> 20:49.772
More than anything.

20:49.882 --> 20:51.316
Well, then, go to New York.

20:51.417 --> 20:52.475
Give it a shot.

20:52.585 --> 20:53.950
New York!

20:54.053 --> 20:55.213
Oh, I don't know, Fonzie.

20:55.321 --> 20:56.481
What if I'm not good enough?

20:56.589 --> 20:58.182
Hey, not good enough.

20:58.290 --> 20:59.690
Who are you talking to?

20:59.792 --> 21:01.191
You want something that bad,

21:01.293 --> 21:03.262
