and take a shot at it.

21:03.362 --> 21:05.092
Not wonder what could've been.

21:05.197 --> 21:06.995
Well, what about my classes?

21:07.099 --> 21:08.464
I'm doing so good now.

21:08.567 --> 21:11.537
Colleen.

21:11.637 --> 21:13.366
You don't study ballet

21:13.472 --> 21:15.099
for that many years to teach it.

21:15.207 --> 21:18.404
You study ballet to perform it.

21:18.511 --> 21:19.910
Bucko.

21:21.814 --> 21:23.577
Cancel the "bucko."

21:26.418 --> 21:28.512
I guess I'm just afraid.

21:28.621 --> 21:29.918
Afraid?

21:30.022 --> 21:31.683
Heyyy.

21:33.392 --> 21:35.122
I've always wanted to.

21:35.227 --> 21:38.663
I really don't have
anything to keep me here

21:38.764 --> 21:41.324
except two azalea bushes.

21:41.433 --> 21:43.425
Let me tell you something,
Colleen, I don't want to sit

21:43.536 --> 21:46.232
across from you sometime
at a table, looking at a chick

21:46.338 --> 21:48.034
who's having second thoughts

21:48.140 --> 21:50.700
about what might have been.

21:50.809 --> 21:52.641
Maybe you're right, Fonzie,
but I...

21:52.745 --> 21:53.644
No, no, no.

21:53.746 --> 21:54.736
No buts.

21:54.847 --> 21:56.645
You just go.

21:56.749 --> 21:58.808
I love the ballet.

21:58.918 --> 22:00.943
- I live for the ballet.
- Oh, wait a minute.

22:01.053 --> 22:03.420
You're not gonna tell me one
of Ralph's jokes now, are you?

22:03.522 --> 22:05.718
No, I really love it.

22:05.824 --> 22:07.725
And I have some girlfriends

22:07.826 --> 22:09.727
