22:09.828 --> 22:11.023
See there?

22:11.130 --> 22:13.189
Then everything is
just perfect, huh?

22:13.299 --> 22:15.358
You go get ready,
we'll celebrate.

22:15.467 --> 22:17.561
I'm so excited!

22:17.670 --> 22:19.570
And maybe even
I can study with him--

22:19.672 --> 22:22.471
Turgenev, the best of them all.

22:25.077 --> 22:27.068
Yeah, we'll celebrate.

22:28.447 --> 22:30.006
Whoa.

22:33.152 --> 22:35.211
Hey, Mr. Best of 'Em All...

22:38.224 --> 22:39.657
...just do me a favor, huh?

22:39.758 --> 22:41.727
Take real good care
of my chick, huh?

22:41.827 --> 22:43.818
Heyyy.

22:51.370 --> 22:53.429
(door opens)

22:55.708 --> 22:57.073
Okay, Fonz.

22:57.176 --> 23:00.145
Here's the keys,
car's downstairs.

